data.description: Nestled in the heart of Yuma this x4 bd/2ba is centrally located to medical, shopping and schools. It beckons with a unique blend of modern comfort and classic charm. Open floor plan with huge living/dining areas and oversized bedrooms. Kitchen with newer appliances includes double ovens, electric cook top, and granite counters. Primary suite has door to amazing outdoor space with covered patio, waterfall, fire pit, and lush grass area. Perfect place to entertain or just relax and enjoy the cooler weather.
